{
  "stem": "935.9",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Make up time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This was my-- my biggest thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The other thing was that I knew that if I would go home, or when I went home, it wouldn't work, because I was not the one who had left.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And even so, with all the love and compassion and understanding, they would look for me, I no longer existed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And therefore, I have always said, you know, Thomas Wolfe, you can't go home again?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, you can.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The question one must ask is should one?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I should not have.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't talk about other people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I should not have gone home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they were looking for me, and I wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And even so, with-- you know, they couldn't do right for me anyway.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was on a different planet altogether.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Totally different planet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wouldn't hear what they said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was with my dead friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember hours and hours I would walk, looking at the stones, thinking, is it true that there are worms underneath?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Would they be where my friends are?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What is underneath there?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or are there little flowers, violets, or pretty flowers for them?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could not-- not that I couldn't relate to life, but I figured, who are these people?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was sitting in a room full of people, and they would talk to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was sitting there, but I wasn't there at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Not at all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It became so bad, that I couldn't walk one day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing wrong with me physically, nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the doctor said that I was terribly anemic and needed 100,000 of those horse shots.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when we came to Sweden, you see, we were-- first of all, again in quarantine.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
